Field Documentation

int32 payloadtype_config_t::nG723Type

G.723.1 rate. There are two bit rates at which G.723.1 can operate.
Valid values are:
0: 6.3 kbit/s (using 24 byte frames) using a MPC-MLQ algorithm (MOS 3.9)
1: 5.3 kbit/s (using 20 byte frames) using an ACELP algorithm (MOS 3.62)

see G7231_RATE

Examples:
conference.c, fxo.c, fxs.c, and rtp.c.
